      {
        "timestamp": "10.02.2025, 14:29:00",
        "from": "Ceren",
        "message": "Hello ,\nWe are excited to announce that after gathering the best boudoir photography projects of 2024selected based on social media engagement, our website, and other channelswe have created a special issue called Best of Boudoir 2024. I am delighted to inform you that your project has been included in this issue.\nTo access your complimentary digital copy and explore additional details, please log in or sign up on our magazine portal using the link below:\nhttps://boudoirinspiration.com/login\nOnce logged in, youll be able to:\n\tSee which issue you are published in\n\tDownload your free digital copy of the issue\n\tView your posted or scheduled editorial(s)\n\tFind links to purchase a print copy (available in both magazine and hardcover book formats)\n\tView and download PDFs of issues in which you have been featured previously\nIf you havent signed up yet, please make sure to register using the email you provided in your release form, and dont forget to enter your credited Instagram handle to see all your publications. Other team members are also welcome to sign up using their Instagram handles to view the project.\nThank you once again for contributing your beautiful artwork to our project. I wish you a wonderful day!\nKind regards,\nCeren"
      }
    ]
  },
